1.4
log
@reduce .Nd to one line and kill .Tn while here
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: xxboot.8,v 1.3 2007/05/31 19:20:04 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2006 Michael Shalayeff
.\" All rights reserved.
